summary:
I'm a person who is committed to his work and his responsibilities, dedicated, with a high sense of respect for people, the environment and the company to which I belong.
At work, I like to work in companies that inspire me to grow professionally and continue to develop myself. The more challenges they place in me, more comfortable I feel.
I have experience in the insurance, energy and retail markets, working in the area of customer service, risks and loyalty.
